item.dc:creator: @i_pk_pjers_i i_pk_pjers_i
item.description:
@i_pk_pjers_i wrote:

[quote=“adu, post:2, topic:219024”]yeah, if your using divine/demonik source make a new run.bat and put this in

set PATH=%PATH%;C:\apache-ant-1.7.0\bin set JAVA_HOME=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_05 ant demonikf2p

thats your f2p world, make sure the version is right in f2pconf.xml

PS- Now you gotta chnage the rank of everyone who cubsribes so that they dont get p2p status right away.[/quote]lol thats the same directory/jdk version i use for java. tho i use \apache-ant-1.7.0\bin without c:\ for apache ant because i installed it where divinepk is installed.

yeah, if your using divine/demonik source make a new run.bat and put this in
